methods.interceptCall:
Note: Java generics information - <ReqT,
RespT>

:param call: io.grpc.ServerCall<ReqT,RespT>
:param headers: io.grpc.Metadata
:param next: io.grpc.ServerCallHandler<ReqT,RespT>
:return: io.grpc.ServerCall.Listener<ReqT>

text:
Interceptor to notice x-deephaven-stream headers in a request and provide them to later parts of BrowserStream
 tooling so that unary and server-streaming calls can be combined into an emulated bidirectional stream.
